high_descs: Go into the kitchen and go to the sink.
Pick up the gray knife on the counter next to the sink.
Turn around and go to the round table with a lettuce on top.
Slice the lettuce on the table.
Turn around and go to the small counter space on the left of the stove.
Place the knife in front of the toaster.
Turn around to go back to the round table on the other side.
Pick up one slice of the lettuce
Turn around and go towards the front of the refrigerator.
Chill the lettuce in the refrigerator and take it out.
Turn around to go back to the counter on the left of stove.
Place the lettuce in front of the toaster next to the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put the knife and the sliced chilled lettuce in front of the toaster,

high_descs: Walk forward and take a right at the fridge and walk across the room to face the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Turn around and walk all the way across the room to face the kitchen table.
Cut the lettuce on the kitchen table.
Turn around and walk all the way across to the counter to the left of the kitchen.
Place the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk all the way across the room to face the kitchen table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the table.
Turn around, walk to the counter and take a left and turn left to face the fridge.
Cool the lettuce in the fridge and remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the counter to the left.
Place the lettuce on the counter to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: To cool a piece of lettuce in the fridge and place it on the counter to the left of the stove.

pick up the knife

turn right towards the gas
drop the knife by the gas

place the cold slice by the gas
